  "Schema": 1,
  "Description": "Build s&box games by talking to Claude. 131 tools to drive the s&box editor through conversation — GameObjects, scripts, scenes, components, physics, networking, UI, world-gen, lighting & atmosphere, characters, scene layout, scatter & object utilities, type discovery. v1.4.0 adds 32 authoring tools (lights/fog/post-fx, citizens with equip/pose/expression, snap-to-ground/align/distribute/grid-duplicate, scatter_props, find_objects) on a stable base. If you use Claude Code, install the companion plugin: `/plugin marketplace add LouSputthole/Sbox-Claude` then `/plugin install sbox-claude` — it bundles the MCP server registration plus an `sbox-build-feature` skill that codifies the screenshot-driven iteration workflow. See TROUBLESHOOTING.md if anything misbehaves.",
